Managing Partners Limited (MPL) is a multi-disciplined investment house that manages a range of collective investment schemes and regulated mutual funds investing in absolute return and other alternative asset classes. The senior management team has over fifty (50) years of collective experience in asset and mutual fund management.
MPL is a member of The Alternative Investment Management Association Limited (“AIMA”) and is registered in the Cayman Islands where it is recognised by the Cayman Islands Monetary Authority as a mutual fund manager where it manages a number of collective investment schemes and regulated mutual funds. MPL has offices in the United Kingdom, mainland Europe and Switzerland where its subsidiary, MPL Asset Management SA is regulated by the Organisme d´Autorégulation des Gérants de Patrimoine.
